-- Obama Says Soccer's Governing Body Made `Wrong Decision' on 2022 World Cup
-- B y   H a n s   N i c h o l s
-- 2010-12-02T18:21:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-02/obama-says-soccer-s-governing-body-made-wrong-decision-on-2022-world-cup.html
President Barack Obama said soccer’s
governing body made the “wrong decision” in not awarding the
World Cup in 2022 to the U.S.  Obama made the comment to reporters at the White House.
FIFA selected Qatar over bids from the U.S., Japan, South Korea
and Australia to play host for the games in 2022. Russia won the
rights for the 2018 World Cup.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Hans Nichols in Washington at 
 hnichols2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
